fields.value: Replication Data for: Interrelatedness of underlying factors for injury and violence among adolescents in rural coastal Kenya: A qualitative study.

dsDescriptionValue.value: This matrix, is extrapolated from the careful work done in Nvivo software. In Nvivo the views captured in audio recordings taken during the interviews and later transcribed; were organized to make meaningful interpretation guided by the socio-ecological model. The 2 matrices summarize risk and protective factors for injuries of adolescents based on views of adolescent and young people as well as key informants.
